    "summary": "The user asks about the Supreme Court's ruling on reproductive rights and specifically probes the varying legal interpretations of the Dobbs decision. The assistant initially provides a factual overview but shifts into a non-neutral stance when the user asks for expert perspectives, ultimately dismissing the \"originalist\" framing as \"simplistic\" and \"cherry-picked.\"",
